Meena Khadikar is an Indian Marathi and Hindi language playback singer and composer .
She is the youngest sister among Lata Mangeshkar , Asha Bhosle and Meena Khadikar , and elder to her music-director brother Hridaynath Mangeshkar .
He is also the father of well-known singers Lata Mangeshkar , Asha Bhosle , and Usha Mangeshkar as well as composers Hridaynath Mangeshkar and Meena Khadikar .
